name: Reserve Currency Dogs
description: Welcome to Reserve Currency Dogs, the ultimate memecoin revolution! With $RCD, there are no buy or sell taxes, and our roadmap is packed with exciting milestones and community rewards. Join us as we blend humour with crypto savvy to create the next big memecoin sensation!
